    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-02-04T10:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-02-04T10:00:00-05:00" n="215"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d215">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/2382</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GJW1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gerard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-02-04T16:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 4, 1916, 4 p. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received February 5, 1.10 p. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3437. Informed by two German reporters, friends of mine, that soon a manifesto
                    will be issued to all neutral nations saying that enemy merchant vessels will be
                    sunk without notice; this being based on alleged orders from British Admiralty
                    alleged to have been found on British merchant vessels instructing captains to
                    fire on submarines at sight.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GJW1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Gerard</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
